information: Welcome to your Austrian fresh meat partner! First-class quality in beef and pork meat and byproducts, fresh or frozen are the source of our success in exports markets around the world. Our customers range from internationally operating processing companies, big chain stores to highly innovative butchers in our village. There are good reasons for the high amount of target markets and the outstanding variety of customers: Absolute customer focus: Individual cutting and offers which will satisfy your demands regarding quantity, packaging and delivery date. Wide product rangeRanging from half a cow or pig to ready self-service packaging.
